---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

// If your image is in /public/images/about-hero.jpg, use the string path below.
// If it's in src/assets, import it like:
// import aboutHero from "../assets/about-hero.jpg";
// and then set imageSrc = aboutHero.
---

<Layout>
  <!-- Page header -->
  <section class="border-b border-white/5 bg-zinc-950/60">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 sm:py-16">
      <h1 class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-4xl text-orange-400">
        About CRT
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-3 max-w-3xl text-zinc-300">
        More about us at 
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Image + intro -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-10 sm:py-14">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-10 items-center">
      <figure class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-zinc-900/50 shadow-lg">
        <img
          src="/about-tp.jpg"
          alt="CRT members volunteering at OC MakerFaire."
          class="h-72 w-full object-cover md:h-[420px]"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
        />
      </figure>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl sm:text-2xl text-orange-400">
          Our Mission
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed maximus viverra nunc, 
          in lobortis sapien. Vivamus iaculis, ante nec semper gravida, libero lorem pulvinar ligula, 
          eget eleifend enim quam sit amet massa. Maecenas sit amet sollicitudin nulla. Nullam ullamcorper 
          lobortis ante, sit amet accumsan libero pretium sed.
        </p>
